    HDBManager
    The HDBManager class represents a user with administrative privileges responsible for managing BTO project listings, approving applications, and overseeing officer registrations within the BTO Management System.

    The HDBManagerUI class serves as the command-line interface for users with the HDB Manager role in the BTO Management System.
    HDBOfficer
    The HDBOfficer class represents a user assigned to manage flat booking and enquiry resolution in the BTO Management System.
    HDBOfficerUI
    The HDBOfficerUI class defines the command-line interface for officers in the BTO Management System.
    Main
